<exercise checkit-seed="0048" checkit-slug="M4" checkit-title="Finding a matrix inverse">
  <statement>
    <p>Show how to find the inverse of the matrix <m>A= \left[\begin{array}{cccc}
-3 &amp; -2 &amp; -3 &amp; 5 \\
3 &amp; 4 &amp; -5 &amp; 8 \\
3 &amp; 4 &amp; -4 &amp; 7 \\
4 &amp; 3 &amp; 3 &amp; -5
\end{array}\right] </m>.</p>
  </statement>
  <answer>
    <me>A^{-1}= \left[\begin{array}{cccc}
-17 &amp; 1 &amp; 1 &amp; -14 \\
18 &amp; -1 &amp; -1 &amp; 15 \\
-7 &amp; -2 &amp; 3 &amp; -6 \\
-7 &amp; -1 &amp; 2 &amp; -6
\end{array}\right] </me>
  </answer>
</exercise>

